I'm trying to make a spear lunge module but I don't understand why it isn't working

def module spear_lunge
def desc "Spear lunge"

on key_press x if playing {
    if hotbar_has #Spear if hotbar_has #windcharge{
        switch #windcharge
        
        wait 0.30 switch #Spear
            wait 0.01
        switch #windcharge
    }
}